594
00:45:22,470 --> 00:45:24,660
Yun Yurae, nevidela si dnes náhodou Inhu?

595
00:45:24,660 --> 00:45:26,910
Nie, nevidela som ju.

596
00:45:26,910 --> 00:45:29,550
